The Group Head, Marketing and Communications of FirstBank of Nigeria Limited,  Mrs Folake Ani-Mumuney, has won the coveted 2019 “Hallmark Man of the Year In Professional Excellence – Marketing and Corporate Communications’’ Award. The Editorial Board of Business Hallmark Newspapers bestowed the honour on Mrs Ani-Mumuney for her contributions to the development of the marketing and communications industry in Nigeria. “As a consummate professional, you have continued to set milestones in developing the market for financial services as well  as stakeholders communications management. “We note with admiration your successes in recreating and rejuvenating the First Bank branch in the process setting new Industry benchmarks”, the student said. The prestigious “Hallmark Man of the Year” Award” will be presented at a ceremony scheduled for Sunday, November 10, 2019.